Error handling AndroidManifest.xml

which means lots of things are likely to stop working properly.
To prevent losing data, it's recommended that you use "Save As"
to save a separate copy of your sketch, and restart Processing.
Processing only supports a single Activity in the AndroidManifest.xml\nfile. Only the first activity entry with be updated, and you better hope that\'s the right one, smartypants.
